<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Phenil Chauhan — Full Stack & AppSec Engineer</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0a0a0f;
      --surface: #111118;
      --card: #16161f;
      --border: #252535;
      --accent: #00e5ff;
      --accent2: #7c3aed;
      --accent3: #f59e0b;
      --text: #e8e8f0;
      --muted: #7a7a99;
      --green: #10b981;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1.2rem 4rem;
      background: rgba(10,10,15,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-cta {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--bg);
      background: var(--accent); padding: 0.5rem 1.3rem;
      border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

    /* HERO */
    #hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid; place-items: center;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      padding: 8rem 4rem 4rem;
    }
    .hero-grid-bg {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      opacity: 0.3;
    }
    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute; top: 20%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 600px; height: 400px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0,229,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 900px; }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--accent);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.3);
      padding: 0.35rem 1rem; border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
    }
    .hero-badge::before {
      content: ''; width: 6px; height: 6px;
      background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%;
      animation: pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(1.4); }
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.0;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
    }
    h1 span.accent { color: var(--accent); }
    h1 span.dim { color: var(--muted); }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 600px; margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both;
    }
    .hero-sub strong { color: var(--text); }
    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg);
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.85rem 2rem; border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,229,255,0.3); }
    .btn-ghost {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.85rem 2rem; border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
    .hero-stats {
      display: flex; gap: 3rem; margin-top: 4rem;
      padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.4s ease both;
    }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--accent); line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.2rem; }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* SECTIONS */
    section { padding: 6rem 4rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-label {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--accent);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }
    .section-desc { color: var(--muted); max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .divider { width: 100%; height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin: 0 auto; }

    /* ABOUT */
    #about .about-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start;
    }
    .about-text p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .about-text p strong { color: var(--text); }
    .about-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .tag {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem; padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px;
      color: var(--muted); background: var(--card);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .contact-card {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem;
    }
    .contact-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .contact-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .contact-item a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .contact-item a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .contact-icon {
      width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 6px;
      background: rgba(0,229,255,0.1);
      display: grid; place-items: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem; flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* EXPERIENCE */
    #experience { max-width: 1100px; }
    .timeline { position: relative; }
    .timeline::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
      width: 2px; background: var(--border);
    }
    .exp-item {
      padding-left: 2.5rem; padding-bottom: 3rem; position: relative;
    }
    .exp-item::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; left: -5px; top: 4px;
      width: 12px; height: 12px;
      background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--bg), 0 0 0 5px rgba(0,229,255,0.2);
    }
    .exp-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .exp-title {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text);
    }
    .exp-date {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--accent);
      background: rgba(0,229,255,0.08);
      padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.2);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .exp-company {
      font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--accent2);
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .exp-bullets { list-style: none; }
    .exp-bullets li {
      font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted);
      padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 1.2rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .exp-bullets li::before {
      content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0;
      color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.75rem;
    }
    .exp-bullets li strong { color: var(--text); }
    .exp-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; margin-top: 0.8rem; }
    .exp-tag {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.68rem; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
      background: rgba(124,58,237,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.25);
      color: #a78bfa; border-radius: 3px;
    }

    /* SKILLS */
    #skills .skills-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .skill-card {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.8rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    .skill-card:hover { border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.3); transform: translateY(-3px); }
    .skill-card-icon {
      font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .skill-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    .skill-list { list-style: none; }
    .skill-list li {
      font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted);
      padding: 0.2rem 0;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    }
    .skill-list li::before { content: '# '; color: var(--accent); }

    /* CERTS */
    #certs .certs-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .cert-card {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.9rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .cert-card:hover { border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.3); }
    .cert-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px; flex-shrink: 0;
      background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.2);
      border-radius: 6px; display: grid; place-items: center;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .cert-name { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
    .cert-issuer { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 3rem 4rem;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      max-width: 100%; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.82rem;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--accent);
    }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .footer-links a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
      #hero { padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
      #about .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-stats { gap: 1.5rem; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
      .exp-header { flex-direction: column; }
    }

    /* SCROLL REVEAL */
    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease; }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">PC.</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#certs">Certs</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="mailto:chauhanphenil@gmail.com" class="nav-cta">Hire Me →</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero" style="max-width:100%; padding:8rem 4rem 4rem;">
  <div class="hero-grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-badge">Available for new opportunities</div>
    <h1>
      <span class="dim">Hi, I'm</span><br>
      <span class="accent">Phenil</span> Chauhan
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      <strong>Full Stack & Application Security Engineer</strong> with 6+ years building
      scalable enterprise systems. Expert in <strong>Node.js, React.js, Vue.js</strong>
      — with deep focus on <strong>OWASP standards, penetration testing & AI-driven security</strong>.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-buttons">
      <a href="#experience" class="btn-primary">View Experience ↓</a>
      <a href="mailto:chauhanphenil@gmail.com" class="btn-ghost">📧 Contact Me</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/phenil-chauhan-3b400617b/" target="_blank" class="btn-ghost">LinkedIn ↗</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">6+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Years Experience</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">10+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Enterprise Projects</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">17+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Certifications</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">∞</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Lines of Secure Code</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about" class="reveal">
  <div class="section-label">// about me</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Security-First Developer<br>Based in Mumbai 🇮🇳</h2>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>I'm a <strong>Cybersecurity-focused Full Stack Developer</strong> with 6+ years of experience designing and shipping scalable, secure web applications for enterprise clients across aviation, healthcare, retail analytics, and food-tech.</p>
      <p>My expertise spans <strong>Node.js, React.js, Vue.js, and Laravel</strong> on the development side — and <strong>Burp Suite, OWASP ZAP, Nmap, SQLMap</strong> on the security side. I bridge the gap between building and hardening.</p>
      <p>I'm currently expanding into <strong>Web Application Penetration Testing, Vulnerability Assessment, Cloud Security</strong>, and <strong>AI-assisted security automation</strong> using tools like PentestGPT, GitHub Copilot, and Google Vertex AI.</p>
      <p>Seeking roles in <strong>Application Security, Product Security, or Senior Full Stack</strong> where I can leverage 6+ years of dev experience + security knowledge to build resilient, production-grade systems.</p>
      <div class="about-tags">
        <span class="tag">Mumbai, India</span>
        <span class="tag">MCA Graduate</span>
        <span class="tag">OWASP Champion</span>
        <span class="tag">AI Security Research</span>
        <span class="tag">Open to Remote</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-card">
      <h3>📬 Get in Touch</h3>
      <div class="contact-item">
        <div class="contact-icon">✉️</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);">Email</div>
          <a href="mailto:chauhanphenil@gmail.com">chauhanphenil@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-item">
        <div class="contact-icon">📱</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);">Phone</div>
          <a href="tel:+918108789081">+91 81087 89081</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-item">
        <div class="contact-icon">💼</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);">LinkedIn</div>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/phenil-chauhan-3b400617b/" target="_blank">phenil-chauhan</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-item">
        <div class="contact-icon">📍</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);">Location</div>
          <span style="color:var(--text);font-size:0.85rem;">Mumbai, Maharashtra, India</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- EXPERIENCE -->
<section id="experience" class="reveal">
  <div class="section-label">// work history</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">6+ Years of<br>Shipping & Securing</h2>
  <p class="section-desc">From food delivery startups to global aviation logistics — building and hardening systems at scale.</p>

  <div class="timeline">

    <!-- Allied Aviation -->
    <div class="exp-item">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <div class="exp-title">Senior Software Developer</div>
        <div class="exp-date">Dec 2025 — March 2026</div>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-company">Allied Aviation India Pvt. Ltd. | Mumbai</div>
      <ul class="exp-bullets">
        <li>Increased system scalability by <strong>35%</strong> by re-architecting backend with Node.js/Express to handle high-concurrency aviation logistics</li>
        <li>Reduced API response times by <strong>40%</strong> through SQL query optimization and Redis caching, supporting real-time analytics dashboards</li>
        <li>Eliminated <strong>100% of high-risk vulnerabilities</strong> (XSS, Insecure Endpoints) via Burp Suite and OWASP ZAP security audits</li>
        <li>Implemented <strong>JWT, OAuth, RBAC</strong> secure authentication mechanisms and HTTP security headers (CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options)</li>
        <li>Developed React.js dashboards integrated with Node.js APIs and PostgreSQL for real-time reporting</li>
        <li>Collaborated with QA and DevOps teams on secure deployment practices and vulnerability mitigation</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="exp-tags">
        <span class="exp-tag">Node.js</span><span class="exp-tag">React.js</span>
        <span class="exp-tag">PostgreSQL</span><span class="exp-tag">Redis</span>
        <span class="exp-tag">Burp Suite</span><span class="exp-tag">OWASP ZAP</span>
        <span class="exp-tag">JWT</span><span class="exp-tag">RBAC</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- NielsenIQ -->
    <div class="exp-item">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <div class="exp-title">Full Stack Developer</div>
        <div class="exp-date">Jun 2024 — Jun 2025</div>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-company">NIELSENIQ India Pvt. Ltd. | Mumbai</div>
      <ul class="exp-bullets">
        <li>Improved data retrieval speed by <strong>25%</strong> for real-time reporting by refactoring Vue.js frontends and optimizing Laravel Eloquent queries</li>
        <li>Hardened application security implementing secure authentication (JWT, OAuth) and RBAC across multiple services</li>
        <li>Built React.js + Node.js analytics dashboards integrated with PostgreSQL for real-time data visualization</li>
        <li>Tested against <strong>OWASP Top 10</strong> vulnerabilities including XSS, CSRF, authentication weaknesses, and insecure API configurations</li>
        <li>Configured HTTP security headers (CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options) to mitigate browser-based attacks</li>
        <li>Integrated REST APIs with real-time data updates using Vuex and WebSockets</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="exp-tags">
        <span class="exp-tag">Vue.js</span><span class="exp-tag">Laravel</span>
        <span class="exp-tag">Node.js</span><span class="exp-tag">React.js</span>
        <span class="exp-tag">WebSockets</span><span class="exp-tag">Redis</span>
        <span class="exp-tag">OWASP Top 10</span><span class="exp-tag">Postman</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- One Health Assist -->
    <div class="exp-item">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <div class="exp-title">Senior Laravel Developer</div>
        <div class="exp-date">Apr 2024 — Jun 2024</div>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-company">ONE HEALTH ASSIST | Mumbai</div>
      <ul class="exp-bullets">
        <li>Launched a high-availability <strong>Telehealth platform</strong> supporting 24/7 video consultations via WebRTC and Laravel real-time tracking</li>
        <li>Built a secure role-based admin panel for managing doctors, patients, schedules, and consultations</li>
        <li>Implemented RESTful APIs for mobile and web with OTP verification, email notifications, and payment gateway integration</li>
        <li>Optimized Laravel Eloquent queries and database structure for reduced server response time</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="exp-tags">
        <span class="exp-tag">Laravel</span><span class="exp-tag">WebRTC</span>
        <span class="exp-tag">REST APIs</span><span class="exp-tag">RBAC</span>
        <span class="exp-tag">Payment Gateway</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Foozo -->
    <div class="exp-item">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <div class="exp-title">PHP Developer</div>
        <div class="exp-date">Oct 2023 — Nov 2023</div>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-company">FOOZO FOODS AND SERVICES PVT. LTD. | Mumbai</div>
      <ul class="exp-bullets">
